de: Amendment to the Loan Agreement concluded on December 5th, 1980, between the Federal Office for External Economic Affairs (FOEEA) and the Industrial Development Bank Limited (IDB) on the granting fo a mixed credit and to the Guarantee Agreement between the Swiss Confederation and the Republic of Kenya, dated 11th of December, 1981 (Texte original envoyé aux AF le 7.6.1994)- Copie Doc.jur. - 13-05-1994 - Kreditabkommen zwischen dem Bundesamt für Aussenwirtschaft, Bern, namens des Schweizerischen Bundesrates, und der Bank für industrielle Entwicklung (BIE; Industrial Development Bank Limited, IDB), einer in der Republik Kenia bestehenden Aktiengesellschaft mit Sitz in Nairobi, über die Gewährung eines Mischkredits (Kreditlinie)
en: Amendment to the Loan Agreement concluded on December 5th, 1980, between the Federal Office for External Economic Affairs (FOEEA) and the Industrial Development Bank Limited (IDB) on the granting fo a mixed credit and to the Guarantee Agreement between the Swiss Confederation and the Republic of Kenya, dated 11th of December, 1981 (Texte original envoyé aux AF le 7.6.1994)- Copie Doc.jur. - 13-05-1994 - Loan Agreement between the Federal Office for External Economic Affairs, Berne, representing the Swiss Federal Council, and the Industrial Development Bank Limited (IDB), a limited company incorporated in the Republic of Kenya and having its registered office at Nairobi, on the granting of a mixed credit (line of credit)
fr: Amendment to the Loan Agreement concluded on December 5th, 1980, between the Federal Office for External Economic Affairs (FOEEA) and the Industrial Development Bank Limited (IDB) on the granting fo a mixed credit and to the Guarantee Agreement between the Swiss Confederation and the Republic of Kenya, dated 11th of December, 1981 (Texte original envoyé aux AF le 7.6.1994)- Copie Doc.jur. - 13-05-1994 - Accord de prêt entre l'Office fédéral des affaires économiques extérieures, Berne, au nom du Conseil fédéral suisse et la Banque de Développement Industriel (BDI) S.A., constituée en République du Kenya et ayant son siège social à Nairobi, concernant l'octroi d'un crédit mixte (ligne de crédit)
